203
00:33:43,540 --> 00:33:47,660
So the conditioning which is there,
the existing conditioning has to be

204
00:33:47,660 --> 00:33:49,300
changed, altered, destroyed.

205
00:33:50,580 --> 00:33:55,700
And to change the existing, we need the
power of Durga and that is our sankalp

206
00:33:55,700 --> 00:33:56,200
shakti.

