02:00:27,610 --> 02:00:29,950
And the journalist said, you don't have a
water bottle.

948
02:00:29,950 --> 02:00:30,390
You don't have a watch on.

949
02:00:30,670 --> 02:00:34,310
How did you tell the time?

950
02:00:37,230 --> 02:00:39,630
And he said, I just came a few days early.

951
02:00:41,710 --> 02:00:43,910
And he said, yeah, but you have no water.

952
02:00:44,150 --> 02:00:45,630
We're in the middle of the desert.

953
02:00:45,730 --> 02:00:46,470
How did you survive?

954
02:00:49,630 --> 02:00:51,870
And the boy said, there's a water bird.

955
02:00:52,030 --> 02:00:53,090
I just call it.

956
02:00:53,530 --> 02:00:56,130
And then it comes and I follow it back to
water.

957
02:01:01,530 --> 02:01:06,810
And at that moment, the journalist was
forced to ask himself, who is more

958
02:01:06,810 --> 02:01:07,090
intelligent?

959
02:01:13,410 --> 02:01:16,830
And this was the question to my high
school students, who is more intelligent,

960
02:01:17,030 --> 02:01:20,190
us now or people from 2,000 years ago?

961
02:01:20,190 --> 02:01:23,870
And this was the question to my high
school students, who is more intelligent,

962
02:01:24,130 --> 02:01:27,730
us now or people from 2,000 years ago?

963
02:01:27,730 --> 02:01:36,150
We often don't ask ourselves and we rarely
ask our children to really think about

964
02:01:36,150 --> 02:01:39,830
where so much of where our current life
has come from.

965
02:01:39,890 --> 02:01:41,410
Who created these solutions?

966
02:01:44,530 --> 02:01:47,630
We rarely ask ourselves or our children.

967
02:01:47,630 --> 02:01:59,770
Very few solutions are human solutions.

968
02:02:02,830 --> 02:02:05,630
They're poor copies of nature.

969
02:02:07,590 --> 02:02:11,970
We now use that scientifically in the
science of biomimicry.

970
02:02:16,270 --> 02:02:17,610
And the solutions that come from that are
very rare.

971
02:02:17,630 --> 02:02:21,210
And the solutions that come from that are
far more evolved than what our limited

972
02:02:21,210 --> 02:02:22,330
minds come up with.

973
02:02:28,230 --> 02:02:29,750
Lajja, modesty.

974
02:02:33,510 --> 02:02:34,750
Shanti, peace.

975
02:02:37,510 --> 02:02:38,730
Shraddha, faith.

976
02:02:42,310 --> 02:02:43,890
Kanti, beauty.

977
02:02:45,850 --> 02:02:47,970
Lakshmi, prosperity.

978
02:02:50,210 --> 02:02:52,890
Vritti, activity or modification.

979
02:02:55,830 --> 02:02:57,430
Smriti, memory.

980
02:02:59,470 --> 02:03:00,830
Daya, compassion.

981
02:03:02,910 --> 02:03:04,510
Tushti, contentment.

982
02:03:07,590 --> 02:03:09,130
Matri, mother.

983
02:03:11,490 --> 02:03:13,270
Branti, confusion.

984
02:03:18,730 --> 02:03:20,050
Indriya, senses.

985
02:03:23,030 --> 02:03:27,630
This process we did with the first few
