987
02:03:38,270 --> 02:03:40,450
It's really interesting.

988
02:03:40,450 --> 02:03:44,550
It never gets old, I find.

989
02:03:46,510 --> 02:03:52,030
And so my final thought is, in the same
way that we do body rotation in Yoga

990
02:03:52,030 --> 02:04:05,090
Nidra, you can use this rotation for
seeing where you feel and experience these

