1005
02:06:15,320 --> 02:06:21,140
With our awareness on her in this form,
we chant the mantra Aum to her.

1006
02:06:26,880 --> 02:06:29,020
Followed by Aum Shanti.

1007
02:06:33,640 --> 02:06:36,100
Inhale to chant the mantra Aum.

1008
02:06:36,100 --> 02:06:42,800
Inhale to chant the mantra Aum.

1009
02:07:06,480 --> 02:07:07,240
Bring

1010
